aining budget\n","- Shows a warning if budget is negative\n","\n","### 💡 Pro Tip: Be specific about requirements!"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"id":"74e672e3","metadata":{"id":"74e672e3","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/","height":157},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772183587605,"user_tz":-480,"elapsed":18,"user":{"displayName":"Rahul Naroti","userId":"00616741918388541541"}},"outputId":"0aa490fc-ac3c-407a-c6a0-fa8e0b26e7c1"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":["'\\nMy Budget Tracker Prompt:\\nCreate a Python program that does the following:\\n1.  Asks the user for their monthly income.\\n2.  Prompts the user to enter up to 3 expenses, asking for each expense amount individually.\\n3.  Calculates the total expenses.\\n4.  Calculates the remaining budget by subtracting total expenses from the monthly income.\\n5.  Prints the monthly income, total expenses, and the remaining budget.\\n6.  If the remaining budget is negative, display a warning message indicating that the user is over budget.\\n7.  Ensure that all numerical inputs are handled gracefully, asking the user to re-enter if invalid input is provided.\\n'"],"application/vnd.google.colaboratory.intrinsic+json":{"type":"string"}},"metadata":{},"execution_count":5}],"source":["# TASK: Write your detailed prompt for the budget tracker\n","\"\"\"\n","My Budget Tracker Prompt:\n","Create a Python program that does the following:\n","1.  Asks the user for their monthly income.\n","2.  Prompts the user to enter up to 3 expenses, asking for each expense amount individually.\n","3.  Calculates the total expenses.\n","4.  Calculates the remaining budget by subtracting total expenses from the monthly income.\n","5.  Prints the monthly income, total expenses, and the remaining budget.\n","6.  If the remaining budget is negative, display a warning message indicating that the user is over budget.\n","7.  Ensure that all numerical inputs are handled gracefully, asking the user to re-enter if invalid input is provided.\n","\"\"\""]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"4bcfacf4","metadata":{"id":"4bcfacf4"},"source":["### Paste and Test Your AI-Generated Budget Tracker"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"id":"2501e778","metadata":{"id":"2501e778","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1771298585153,"user_tz":-480,"elapsed":52546,"user":{"displayName":"Rahul Naroti","userId":"00616741918388541541"}},"outputId":"b7889143-22bf-49a9-81d8-2f4dcf48ff96"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Enter your monthly income: 3000\n","\n","Enter up to 3 expenses. Enter 0 or an empty value to stop adding expenses.\n","Enter expense 1 amount: 1500\n","Enter expense 2 amount: 1000\n","Enter expense 3 amount: 500\n","\n","------------------------------\n","Monthly Income: $3,000.00\n","Total Expenses: $3,000.00\n","Remaining Budget: $0.00\n","------------------------------\n"]}],"source":["# AI-GENERATED BUDGET TRACKER CODE\n","\n","# Function to get a valid numerical input from the user\n","def get_valid_number_input(prompt_message, error_message=\"Error: Please enter a valid number.\", min_value=0):\n","    while True:\n","        try:\n","            value = float(input(prompt_message))\n","            if value < min_value:\n","                print(f\"Error: Value cannot be negative. Please enter a non-negative number.\")\n","                continue\n","            return value\n","        except ValueError:\n","            print(error_message)\n","\n","# 1. Ask for the user's monthly income\n","monthly_income = get_valid_number_input(\"Enter your monthly income: \")\n","\n","expenses = []\n","total_expenses = 0\n","\n","# 2. Prompt the user to enter up to 3 expenses\n","print(\"\\nEnter up to 3 expenses. Enter 0 or an empty value to stop adding expenses.\")\n","for i in range(1, 4):\n","    expense_amount = get_valid_number_input(f\"Enter expense {i} amount: \", min_value=0)\n","    if expense_amount == 0:\n","        break\n","    expenses.append(expense_amount)\n","    total_expenses += expense_amount\n","\n","# 3. Calculate the remaining budget\n","remaining_budget = monthly_income - total_expenses\n","\n","# 4. Print the monthly income, total expenses, and the remaining budget\n","print(\"\\n\" + \"-\" * 30)\n","print(f\"Monthly Income: ${monthly_income:,.2f}\")\n","print(f\"Total Expenses: ${total_expenses:,.2f}\")\n","print(f\"Remaining Budget: ${remaining_budget:,.2f}\")\n","print(\"-\" * 30)\n","\n","# 5. Display a warning if the remaining budget is negative\n","if remaining_budget < 0:\n","    print(\"WARNING: You are over budget!\")\n","    print(f\"You need an additional ${abs(remaining_budget):,.2f} to cover your expenses.\")\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"f541d525","metadata":{"id":"f541d525"},"source":["### 🐛 Debugging and Refinement"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"id":"3f624a27","metadata":{"id":"3f624a27","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1771298909742,"user_tz":-480,"elapsed":58,"user":{"displayName":"Rahul Naroti","userId":"00616741918388541541"}},"outputId":"6a44ec24-3dcb-4281-f6e9-0921169deb9d"},"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["🔧 DEBUGGING NOTES:\n","- Issue 1: No major issues found; the AI-generated code worked as expected.\n","- Fix 1: N/A\n"]}],"source":["# Document any issues and fixes\n","issues_found = [\n","    \"Issue 1: No major issues found; the AI-generated code worked as expected.\",\n","    \"Fix 1: N/A\"\n","    # Add more as needed\n","]\n","\n","print(\"🔧 DEBUGGING NOTES:\")\n","for item in issues_found:\n","    print(f\"- {item}\")"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"id":"0772261d","metadata":{"id":"0772261d"},"outputs":[],"source":["# REFINED VERSION - Your Working Budget Tracker\n","# [Paste your corrected/improved code here]"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"ca842a66